  "task": "# Relay stage 1: Ideate\nTask: show-total-cost-per-day-in-archive-view\nWorking directory: /tmp/nix-shell.mK1bQ4/visual-relay/wt/fbb5c78605a5/plan-20260630215331/show-total-cost-per-day-in-archive-view\n\n## Task input\n# Show Total Cost Per Day in Archive View\n\nThe archive view currently splits tasks per day/date, and it lists each task within those groups, with each task showing a cost.\n\nI also want the day group name to include the total cost for that day.\n\nFor example, it might show \"Today ($1.54)\" and \"Yesterday ($0.21)\".\n\n## Manifest\n(not set yet)\n\n## Task context\n### Screenshot 2026-06-30 at 2.43.34\u202fPM.png (83306 bytes, not inlined)\n\n## Prior stages\n\n\nEnd your reply with a single fenced ```json block, nothing after it, matching: { \"summary\": string, \"options\": string[] }",
